__commentLine01: This file is for specifying domains you may not want to be auto-selected
__commentLine02: when the emulator is started. To use it, enter the name of the domain/VMD
__commentLine03: that you wish to blacklist as it appears in the memory domains table. If
__commentLine04: you are using more than one line, be sure to add a comma (,) to the end
__commentLine05: of every line, EXCEPT FOR THE LAST.
